'''葛飾北齋'''（Katsushika Hokusai），[[1760年]]出世，[[1849年]][[5月10號]]過身<ref name="lane">Nagata, Seiji. ''Hokusai: Genius of the Japanese Ukiyo-e''. Kodansha, Tokyo, 1999.</ref>，係隻[[日本]]江戶時代嗰藝術家、浮世繪畫家、版畫家，佢也係日本嗰中國畫嗰尖端畫家。<ref>Daniel Atkison and Leslie Stewart. "[http://www.csuchico.edu/art/contrapposto/contrapposto99/pages/essays/themefloating/hohusaimnt.html Life and Art of Katsushika Hokusai]" in ''From the Floating World: Part II: Japanese Relief Prints'', catalogue of an exhibition produced by [[California State University, Chico]]. Retrieved 9 July 2007; [http://web.archive.org/web/20021108104201/http://www.csuchico.edu/art/contrapposto/contrapposto99/pages/essays/themefloating/hohusaimnt.html archive link]</ref>佢嗰代表作係《富嶽三十六景》（Fugaku Sanjūrokkei）、《北齋漫畫》（Hokusai Manga）。

